size_change <- lob_a %>%
  filter(YEAR ==  2012 | YEAR == 2017) %>% 
  group_by(SITE, YEAR) %>% 
  summarize(
    lob_mean = round(mean(SIZE), 2),
    lob_sd = round(sd(SIZE), 2)
  ) %>% 
  mutate (year = as.character(YEAR)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = SITE, y = lob_mean)) +
  geom_col(aes(fill = year), position = "dodge")+
  coord_flip()+
  theme_pubr()

size_change
